data.description: Adorable and updated North Dallas home just steps from the Preston Ridge Trail. Fantastic, open floor plan featuring two living areas, three bedrooms, two and a half baths, large kitchen, and two-car garage, epoxy floor. Updates include appliances, countertops, wood-look ceramic floors, half bath vanity, paint throughout, AC unit. Home is conveniently located between the Dallas North Tollway, Central Expressway, the George Bush Turnpike, and is zoned to Plano ISD.
